description._content: Catalog #: 09_01235 Title: H. Murray Gibson Special Collection Photo St. Louis Missouri Additional Information: Man identified as 'Jean DeFlandre' Terminal Manager of Greyhound Lines St. Louis, Missouri. Handwritten inscription ""taken before start of St. Louis Chamber of Commerce Good Will Charter"", H. Murray Gibson was a bus driver for the Greyhound bus company. He was also an aviation enthusiast who took flying lessons throughout the 1930s. Corporation Name: Greyhound Lines, Inc Tags: H.
